This script backs up a source directory to local another directory
by rsync. It supports history and reduce size by hard link like
Mac OS's Time Machine.

= How to install =

1. Copy etc/logroated.d/backup to /etc/logroated.d/backup
2. Copy etc/sysconfig/backup to /etc/sysconfig/backup
3. Copy 00-bacup.cron to /etc/cron.daily
4. Modify /etc/sysconfig/backup
